{
  "stem": "21978.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, why don't you shoot that one who has got the cabin?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eventually, we were given a cabin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at night, I got out of the bed-- of the bunk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stood in water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I thought we are sinking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I [INAUDIBLE] my husband.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not sinking ship.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the pantry next to our cabin, there was leaking tap.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the water was underneath.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So we had our adventures.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was a very nice voyage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When we came here, we were met by bank manager with bank we were dealing with, and a friend who was here before us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Otherwise, we haven't had anybody here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they brought us to some boarding house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were complaining that it is cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they said, wait five minutes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You are in Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In five minutes, it will change.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The boarding house was a shock, because it was awful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I went in the kitchen to see what-- dirty-- people had for breakfast, sausages and bacon.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it was all greasy and everything was dirty.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we made haste.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we got a flat somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we established ourselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Our-- my husband got a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And eventually, Annetta-- we, we got a house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were searching for a house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We had a flat originally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we made friends through a Jewish congregation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Our children made us to make friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "As you have children, they meet, meet the parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we have friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We are friends for life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we looked for house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I was with the children in the flat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And my husband came in with a friend who was living here and said, come and have a look at a house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we came to Norbert Street in Balwyn.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
